            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>Python 3.9+ kurulu olmali</strong>
                <p>Terminalde kontrol edin:</p>
                <pre class="docs-code">python --version</pre>
                <p>Kurulu degilse:</p>
                <pre class="docs-code">winget install Python.Python.3.12</pre>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">2</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
