    <!-- BOLUM 4: Adim 3 — API Credential'lari -->
    <!-- ================================================================== -->
    <div class="docs-card" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent-gold);">
        <h2 class="docs-title">4. Adim 3 — API Credential'lari</h2>

        <div class="docs-info">
            <strong>Onemli Not:</strong> Polymarket web arayuzundeki "Relayer API Keys" bolumu farkli bir seydir.
            Bizim sistemin ihtiyaci olan CLOB API credential'larini Python SDK ile almalisiniz.
        </div>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Private Key Alma (MetaMask'tan)</h3>

        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">1</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>MetaMask uzantisini acin</strong>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">2</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>Ustte hesap adina tiklayin</strong>
                <p>Hesap listesi acilir.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">3</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>Hesabin yanindaki 3 noktaya (⋮) tiklayin</strong>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">4</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>"Hesap ayrintilari" veya "Account Details" secin</strong>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">5</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>"Ozel anahtari goster" (Show Private Key) butonuna tiklayin</strong>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">6</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>MetaMask sifrenizi girin</strong>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">7</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>0x ile baslayan 66 karakterlik string'i kopyalayin</strong>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="docs-warning">
            <strong>DIKKAT:</strong> Private key'inizi kimseyle paylasmayın. Bu anahtar cuzdaninizdaki tum varliklara erisim saglar.
        </div>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">API Key + Secret + Passphrase Alma</h3>
        <p>Terminalde asagidaki komutu calistirin:</p>
        <pre class="docs-code">python -c "from py_clob_client.client import ClobClient; client = ClobClient(host='https://clob.polymarket.com', key='0xSENIN_PRIVATE_KEYIN', chain_id=137); creds = client.create_or_derive_api_creds(); print(f'API Key: {creds.api_key}'); print(f'API Secret: {creds.api_secret}'); print(f'Passphrase: {creds.api_passphrase}')"</pre>
        <p><strong>Not:</strong> <code>0xSENIN_PRIVATE_KEYIN</code> yerine MetaMask'tan aldiginiz private key'i yapistirin.</p>
    </div>

