            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">3</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>"Polymarket Credentials" bolumunde 6 alani doldurun</strong>
                <table class="docs-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>#</th>
                            <th>Alan</th>
                            <th>Format</th>
                            <th>Nereden Alinir</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>1</td>
                            <td><strong>API Key</strong></td>
                            <td>UUID formati</td>
                            <td>Python komutu ciktisi</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>2</td>
                            <td><strong>API Secret</strong></td>
                            <td>Base64 string</td>
                            <td>Python komutu ciktisi</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>3</td>
                            <td><strong>Passphrase</strong></td>
                            <td>String</td>
                            <td>Python komutu ciktisi</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>4</td>
                            <td><strong>Wallet Address</strong></td>
                            <td>0x... (42 karakter)</td>
                            <td>MetaMask ana ekran</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>5</td>
                            <td><strong>Private Key</strong></td>
                            <td>0x... (66 karakter)</td>
                            <td>MetaMask > Ozel anahtarlar</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>6</td>
                            <td><strong>Signature Type</strong></td>
                            <td>0</td>
                            <td>Sabit (MetaMask/EOA = 0)</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">4</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>"Kaydet" butonuna tiklayin</strong>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="docs-step">
            <div class="docs-step-number">5</div>
            <div class="docs-step-content">
                <strong>Tum alanlarin yaninda yesil "Dolu" yazdigini kontrol edin</strong>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="docs-example">
            <strong>Guvenlik:</strong> Credential'lar DB'de AES-256 ile sifrelenir. Ekranda asla gosterilmez — sadece "Dolu" veya "Bos" yazar.
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ================================================================== -->
    <!-- BOLUM 6: Adim 5 — Worker'i Baslat -->
    <!-- ================================================================== -->
    <div class="docs-card" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent-blue);">
        <h2 class="docs-title">6. Adim 5 — Worker'i Baslat</h2>
        <p>Komutu calistirin:</p>
        <pre class="docs-code">dotnet run --project src/CryptoTrader/Traxon.CryptoTrader.Worker</pre>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Baslatma Sirasi</h3>
        <pre class="docs-code">
1. Worker baslar
2. PythonSignerHostedService → DB'den credential'lari okur → Python process baslatir
3. Health check: http://127.0.0.1:5099/health
4. Log: "Polymarket signing service started successfully"
5. BufferWarmupService → DB'den mumlari yukler
6. MarketDataWorker → Sinyal uretimi baslar
7. LivePoly engine → Sinyal geldiginde order acar</pre>
    </div>

    <!-- ================================================================== -->
    <!-- BOLUM 7: Teknik Akis — Order Acma -->
    <!-- ================================================================== -->
    <div class="docs-card" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent-purple);">
        <h2 class="docs-title">7. Teknik Akis — Order Acma</h2>
        <pre class="docs-code">
Sinyal uretilir (MarketDataWorker)
    ↓
LivePoly engine sinyal alir
    ├─ GammaAPI'den matching market bul
    ├─ Midpoint fiyat al
    ├─ Market order (FAK) — midpoint fiyattan alınır
    ├─ Position size hesapla (Bakiyenin %2'si, min $1)
    ↓
.NET → HTTP POST http://127.0.0.1:5099/create-and-post
    ↓
Python Signing Service:
    ├─ OrderArgs olustur
    ├─ EIP-712 ile imzala
    ├─ HMAC headers ile CLOB API'ye gonder
    └─ orderId dondur
    ↓
.NET trade'i DB'ye kaydeder, UI'da gosterir</pre>
    </div>

