    <!-- ================================================================== -->
    <!-- BOLUM 9: Sorun Giderme -->
    <!-- ================================================================== -->
    <div class="docs-card" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent-red);">
        <h2 class="docs-title">9. Sorun Giderme</h2>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">"Signing service failed to start"</h3>
        <ul class="docs-list">
            <li>Python kurulu mu? <code>python --version</code></li>
            <li>Paketler kurulu mu? <code>pip install -r scripts/polymarket-signer/requirements.txt</code></li>
            <li>Port 5099 mesgul mu? <code>netstat -an | findstr 5099</code></li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">"Client not initialized - check credentials"</h3>
        <ul class="docs-list">
            <li><code>/config</code> sayfasinda tum alanlar "Dolu" mu?</li>
            <li>Private key 0x ile basliyor ve 66 karakter mi?</li>
            <li>Wallet address 0x ile basliyor ve 42 karakter mi?</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">"Invalid signature"</h3>
        <ul class="docs-list">
            <li>Signature Type dogru mu? MetaMask = 0</li>
            <li>Private key ve wallet address ayni hesaba mi ait?</li>
            <li>py-clob-client guncel mi? <code>pip install --upgrade py-clob-client</code></li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">"Insufficient balance"</h3>
        <ul class="docs-list">
            <li>Polymarket hesabinda yeterli USDC var mi?</li>
            <li>Polygon aginda mi?</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Worker basliyor ama LivePoly trade acmiyor</h3>
        <ul class="docs-list">
            <li><code>appsettings.json</code>'da EnabledEngines icinde "LivePoly" var mi?</li>
            <li>Polymarket'te matching market var mi?</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="docs-subtitle-h3">Python service cokerse ne olur?</h3>
        <ul class="docs-list">
            <li>PaperPoly normal calismaya devam eder</li>
            <li>LivePoly order acamaz ama sistem cokmez</li>
            <li>Worker yeniden baslatilirsa Python service de yeniden baslar</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

